Retrodev v1.0.x
Retro dev environment.

All-in-one project workflow for:
- bitmap conversion
- tiles and sprites extraction
- tile map editing with parallax
- palette solving by constraints
- raster FX generator (CPC)
- integrated Z80/AngelScript editor
- scripted binary export
- build + emulator launch

Targets:
Amstrad CPC/CPC+ (full)
ZX Spectrum, C64, MSX (prepared)

Portable app: unzip and run.
Includes SDK and examples.

More info:
https://github.com/tlotb/retrodev